name: LDR
description:
Communication is the most important thing in relationship.  especially when you are in a long distance relationship;  every minute is so precious when we are communicating with our beloved partner. But the thing that makes it difficult when doing long distance relationships is when the connection is bad.  this is so annoying because the time for us to miss each other becomes disturbed.

This photo was made using cyanotape print media.  The blue color produced by this alternative print is perfect for representing my feelings when having a long distance relationship; distant and cold.
